---
title: Pronto Chicken and Pesto Pasta Verde with Peas, Spinach and Cheese
description: Hey presto! This speedy Pronto Chicken and Pesto Pasta Verde is ready in under 25 minutes. Colourful from green pesto as well as green veg, this dish gives a whole new meaning to eating your greens.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R19_W38_UK_R10434-33_Main_low_2-b1c2036c.jpg
